      ],
      "source": "https://grokipedia.com/page/lake_hiawatha_new_jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Before Europeans, the Lenni‑Lenape people used the area that is now Lake Hiawatha as part of their northern New Jersey territory.",
